<div id="push-onboarding-modal" 
     data-controller="push-onboarding" 
     data-push-onboarding-target="modal"
     class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center px-6">
  
  <!-- Backdrop -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#0F0F13]/80 backdrop-blur-md" data-action="click->push-onboarding#hideModal"></div>

  <!-- Modal Content -->
  <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm app-glass-card border-indigo-500/30 p-8 space-y-6 animate-in fade-in zoom-in duration-300">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-[24px] bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl animate-bounce">
        🔔
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">루파 클럽 앱 알림 설정</h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          내일 아침 확언 알림부터 저녁/밤 루틴 체크까지, <br/>
          휴대폰 알림으로 루틴을 잊지 말고 챙기세요! ✨
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <button data-action="click->push-onboarding#showSetup" 
              class="w-full py-4 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-600 text-white font-black text-sm active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20">
        지금 설정하러 가기
      </button>
      
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <button data-action="click->push-onboarding#hideModal" 
                class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-slate-400 font-bold text-xs hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
          나중에 하기
        </button>
        <button data-action="click->push-onboarding#dismiss" 
                class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 text-slate-600 font-bold text-[10px] hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors">
          다시 보지 않기
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[9px] font-medium text-slate-600 text-center">
      * 아이폰 유저라면 '홈 화면에 추가' 후 설정해 주세요.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
